{"tid":683341,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)衰鬼上帝2 新盜墓者羅拉 奪面雙雄","createTime":"2018-05-29T15:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T19:05:09.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"04f45c8c3e73d446c1b8f491dd92cd59b023574b","tid":683341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:19:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=xKFZhaTraAzHZhA3f9HzVf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=06e66d46\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=xKFZhaTraAzHZhA3f9HzVf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=90d920df\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=xKFZhaTraAzHZhA3f9HzVf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=fde23b42\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/14/Evan_almightymp1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F14%2FEvan_almightymp1.jpg&h=a36b72d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/5f/Tomb_Raider_official_teaser_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F5f%2FTomb_Raider_official_teaser_poster.jpg&h=6b1a7b34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/49/Face_off_movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F49%2FFace_off_movie.jpg&h=9f648169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.原本是電視新聞主播的埃文&middot;貝斯特（Evan Baxter，史提夫&middot;卡爾扮演，為王牌天神1的主播）以「改變世界」為口號，當選紐約州聯邦眾議員；他對事業充滿熱情，極為注重儀表，但對小動物和環境卻缺乏愛心。為了到美國國會履任，他帶著妻子瓊安（Joan）和三個孩子離開舊居布法羅，搬到華盛頓近郊的維吉尼亞州名望山社區（Prestige Crest）。當他雄心勃勃地上任，立即受到資深眾議員恰克&middot;隆恩（Chuck Long）的勸說，連署支持後者起草的土地使用權法案；埃文受寵若驚，很快地答應了.....<br />\n<br />\n2.在蘿拉&middot;卡芙特的父親理查&middot;卡芙特失蹤後，蘿拉靠騎單車送外賣為生，在她出車禍並被帶到警局後，里查德在商業上的夥伴安娜保釋了她，並警告她若不繼承里查德的遺產，那些財產可能會被賣掉。在蘿拉不情願地接受後，她發現一則來自里查的訊息，得知他失蹤前正在調查邪馬台女王卑彌呼。里查要求蘿拉燒掉研究，但蘿拉沒有這麼做，反而踏上尋找父親的旅途<br />\n<br />\n3.肖恩&middot;阿切爾（約翰&middot;屈伏塔）是聯邦調查局的高級探員，20多年的警探生涯辦過無數大案子，可是他終其一生都在追捕奸詐狡猾的恐怖份子卡斯特&middot;特洛伊（尼可拉斯&middot;凱吉） ，無惡不作的卡斯特也正是殺害阿切爾獨生子的凶手，讓阿切爾發誓要親自抓他到案入網。<br />\n終於在多次線人的密告之下，阿切爾終於有機會親自逮捕他歸案，趕在卡斯特與他弟弟波利克斯搭機逃亡之前，將他們繩之以法，在一陣槍戰之後，以損傷七名探員為代價......<br />\n<br />\n11 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=xKFZhaTraAzHZhA3f9HzVf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e337204a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=xKFZhaTraAzHZhA3f9HzVf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=550e5af7\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd6c3db7a3e3d1764948cc41e81b68a76aad41e","tid":683341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3312c152030ff316e2bac06d3811d9fb97620bae","tid":683341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T16:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85ef6e5e2d7d7960ff08ad32cb03a5a6f62858e","tid":683341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c96f9ba46fc45fc454cb4bb6b966dd57a8c35d","tid":683341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T18:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e253561c2e081f8bf14694721c96f5abf9cc82","tid":683341,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T19:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}